\n<Tuberose>Amazing, Rui-san! You've cleared three doors
already?!
\n<Rui>...You're welcome, I suppose.

\n<Tuberose>Yes, yes, it's a celebration. As expected of
someone who possesses the power of Sol.

\n<Tuberose>Normally, even clearing one door is rare, you
know? And yet you've cleared so many! It's
astounding!
\n<Rui>What about you? You seem much happier than I am...
\n<Tuberose>Ehehe, can you tell?
\n<Rui>I see, that's how it is...
\n<Tuberose>Eh?

\n<Rui>There are more doors, aren't there? You're giving
me hope only to let me down later!
\n<Tuberose>No, not at all. I'm genuinely cornered here.

\n<Tuberose>This place... can't really be called a corridor.
All the doors in this room are everything there
is.
\n<Rui>...Yet you seem too composed for that.

\n<Tuberose>It would be a lie to say I'm not anxious. But more
than that, I'm truly happy.

\n<Tuberose>Because with every door you clear, I realize the
"value" of having a woman who would normally be
absolutely unattainable.
\n<Rui>...That's in poor taste.

\n<Tuberose>Mmm, that's nice. Please harbor those negative
feelings towards me.

\n<Tuberose>I'm looking forward to the moment when I'll paint
over them.

\n<Tuberose>Already the lewd crest is corrupting you without
your knowledge, and yet you maintain such a
defiant attitude... It's thrilling.

now, you'd become a puppet on strings... Ahh, it's
thrilling.

\n<Rui>...Enough! I'll quickly clear the last door as
well!
